data.description: Welcome Home to this  cozy well maintain Cape Cod!  The main level offers an eat-in kitchen, updated dining and living room, full bath and a bedroom. Updates include: New Vinyl flooring and light fixtures. The upstairs has a second full bath and three bedrooms, including the master bedroom with a spacious closet. The fourth bedroom has skylight windows and high ceilings. This property offers a walk out basement that includes a wood fireplace, a half bath/laundry room, and a GREAT ENTERTAINMENT AREA with a bar-kitchen area that can also be a potential in-law quarters. You can enjoy music on the intercom system throughout the house. The outside boasts a spacious yard, wrap-around porch, and an additional garage that will be great for storage.  Come look at this Gem! Here's to NEW BEGINNINGS!
